    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "全員集まりました\n私達に話ってなんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone's gathered here\nWhat do you have to say to us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "実は、ライブバトルのことで\nみんなの意見を聞きたいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In fact‚ it's about the live battle\nI want to hear everyone's opinion",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ライブバトルって、次の対戦相手が決まったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For the live battle‚ has the next opponent been decided?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.6333339691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "まだ決定した訳じゃないが\nサニピと戦いたいと名乗りを上げたグループがいる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It hasn't been decided yet\nThere's a group that has nominated themselves to compete with Sunny Peace",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.4000006358
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "サニピの対戦相手に立候補したのは……\nTRINITYAiLEだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The one who has been nominated as Sunny Peace's opponent is…\nTRINITYAiLE",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "トリエル……瑠依さんが、サニピと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE… Rui-san‚ to Sunny Peace…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルが相手なら、みんなも思うところがあるだろう\n対戦するかどうか、みんなで相談して決めてほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If TRINITYAiLE were your opponent‚ there would be something that everyone would think about\nI want everyone to discuss and decide whether or not to fight",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sun-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 44.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "いいえ、相談するまでもありません\nTRINITYAiLEの挑戦、受けて立ちます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ there's no need to discuss it\nWe'll accept‚ TRINITYAiLE's challenge!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
