    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルの頂点を目指すなら\n彼女達は避けては通れない相手よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we're aiming to reach the top of idols‚\nthey're inevitable opponents",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7666646321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.7666646321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロで一緒にトップを目指す\n仲間でライバルだから、ちゃんと向き合いたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're both friends and rivals aiming to reach the top at Hoshimi Prods‚\nso we want to face each other properly",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.5999956767
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "もし逆の立場だったら……\n瑠依さんは私達の挑戦を断ったりしない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If our positions were reversed…\nRui-san wouldn't turn down our challenge…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.9201147,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.2999956767
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "私達は逃げも隠れもしないわ\nトリエルが本気で挑んでくるなら、本気で応えるだけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We won't run away or hide\nIf TRINITYAiLE challenges us seriously‚ we'll respond seriously",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.4999977112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.1666623433
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、私達からもお願いします\nトリエルとライブバトルさせて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ we'd like to ask you to do the same\nLet us have a live battle with TRINITYAiLE!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
