      "text": "はい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9999956767,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 89.3333259582
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.3333259582
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "そうと決まれば、さっそく練習よ。トリエル相手なら\nいくら練習しても安心出来ないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that it's decided‚ let's start practicing right away. No matter how much\nwe practice‚ I can't feel safe against TRINITYAiLE",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.0666643779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.0333259582
    },
    {
