      "text": "ええ、過保護に守る必要なんてなかった……\nみんな強くてたくましい、一人前のアイドルです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ there was no need to be overprotective…\nThey're all strong‚ tough‚ and pull their weight idols",
